world.io

Class OffHeapArray

  • java.lang.Object
    • world.io.OffHeapArray

  • public class OffHeapArray
extends java.lang.Object
    EXTREME WARNING! This class creates an off heap array. These arrays are special because you can ditch all references to them, then increment a pointer to get back to them. They are no managed by the JVM heap, so MAKE SURE YOU CALL THE DESTRUCTOR METHOD OR THERE WILL BE MEMORY LEAKS AND YOU WILL BE PISSED.
    Author:
    Michael Ferolito
